import React from "react"

import Single from "./Single"
import List from "./List"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Link } from "react-router-dom"

function App(props) {
  return (
    <Router>
      <nav>
        <Route exact path="/" component={List} />
      </nav>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
